<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
    <head>
        <meta charset="UTF-8">
        <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
        <title>Pearlworth Foundation School</title>
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/home.css">
        <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@400;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css" integrity="sha512-iecdLmaskl7CVkqkXNQ/ZH/XLlvWZOJyj7Yy7tcenmpD1ypASozpmT/E0iPtmFIB46ZmdtAc9eNBvH0H/ZpiBw==" crossorigin="anonymous" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" />
        <link rel="icon" href="/images/logo.svg" type="image/svg+xml">
    </head>
<body>
    <%- include('partials/header') %>


    <section class="hero">
        <div class="hero-content">
            <h2 class="animate-hero-title">Welcome to Pearlworth Foundation School</h2>
            <p>Nurturing minds, inspiring futures</p>
            <a href="#intro-section" class="cta-button">Learn More</a>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="intro-section" id="intro-section">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="intro-content">
                <p><span class="quote-mark">"</span>If you are looking for a school that nurtures your child's curiosity, independence, sense of community, and love for learning, while providing a strong foundation for future success, then Pearlworth Foundation School is the perfect choice for you!</p>
            </div>
            <div class="intro-features">
                <div class="feature">
                    <i class="fas fa-brain"></i>
                    <h3>Curiosity</h3>
                </div>
                <div class="feature">
                    <i class="fas fa-user-graduate"></i>
                    <h3>Independence</h3>
                </div>
                <div class="feature">
                    <i class="fas fa-users"></i>
                    <h3>Community</h3>
                </div>
                <div class="feature">
                    <i class="fas fa-book-reader"></i>
                    <h3>Love for Learning</h3>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>


    <section class="mission-section">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="mission-content">
                <h2>Our Mission</h2>
                <p class="mission-intro">Our Mission at Pearlworth Foundation School is to partner with families in their responsibility to bring up their children in the harmonious development of their physical, mental, and spiritual capabilities by providing wholesome foundational education.</p>
                <div class="mission-goals">
                    <div class="mission-goal">
                        <i class="fas fa-hands-helping"></i>
                        <h3>Family Partnership</h3>
                        <p>Collaborate with families to support child development</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="mission-goal">
                        <i class="fas fa-balance-scale"></i>
                        <h3>Harmonious Development</h3>
                        <p>Nurture physical, mental, and spiritual growth</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="mission-goal">
                        <i class="fas fa-book"></i>
                        <h3>Wholesome Education</h3>
                        <p>Provide a strong foundational learning experience</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="mission-goal">
                        <i class="fas fa-child"></i>
                        <h3>Child-Centered Approach</h3>
                        <p>Focus on individual growth and potential</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="mission-image">
                <img src="/images/mission.svg" alt="Students engaged in learning">
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="flip-box-section">
        <div class="container">
            <a href="/school_life#activities" class="flip-box">
                <div class="flip-box-inner">
                    <div class="flip-box-front">
                        <i class="fas fa-running flip-box-icon"></i>
                        <h3>Activities</h3>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flip-box-back">
                        <p>Explore our diverse range of extracurricular activities.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </a>
            <a href="/admissions" class="flip-box">
                <div class="flip-box-inner">
                    <div class="flip-box-front">
                        <i class="fas fa-user-graduate flip-box-icon"></i>
                        <h3>Admissions</h3>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flip-box-back">
                        <p>Learn about our admission process and requirements.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </a>
            <a href="/Children_resources/Homework/homework.html" class="flip-box">
                <div class="flip-box-inner">
                    <div class="flip-box-front">
                        <i class="fas fa-book-open flip-box-icon"></i>
                        <h3>Homework</h3>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flip-box-back">
                        <p>Access homework assignments and resources for students.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </a>
            <a href="/Parent_resources/School_circular/school-circular.html" class="flip-box">
                <div class="flip-box-inner">
                    <div class="flip-box-front">
                        <i class="fas fa-newspaper flip-box-icon"></i>
                        <h3>School News</h3>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flip-box-back">
                        <p>Stay updated with the latest news and events at our school.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </a>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="workbooks-section">
        <div class="container">
            <h2>Our Workbooks</h2>
            <div class="workbooks-content">
                <div class="workbooks-image">
                    <img src="/images/workbook.svg" alt="Workbook Preview">
                </div>
                <div class="workbooks-info">
                    <h3>Comprehensive Learning Materials</h3>
                    <p>Our carefully crafted workbooks are designed to enhance your child's learning experience. They cover a wide range of subjects and are tailored to different age groups and learning levels.</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Age-appropriate content</li>
                        <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Engaging exercises and activities</li>
                        <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Aligned with curriculum standards</li>
                        <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Regular updates and improvements</li>
                    </ul>
                    <a href="/workbooks" class="workbooks-cta">Explore Our Workbooks</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="news-section">
        <div class="container">
            <h2>Latest News & Events</h2>
            <div class="news-grid">
                <div class="news-item">
                    <div class="news-image">
                        <img src="/images/football.svg" alt="Annual Sports Day">
                        <div class="news-date">
                            <span class="day">15</span>
                            <span class="month">May</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="news-content">
                        <h3>Annual Sports Day</h3>
                        <p>Join us for our exciting Annual Sports Day on May 15th. Students will showcase their athletic talents!</p>
                        <a href="#" class="read-more">Read More <i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i></a>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="news-item">
                    <div class="news-image">
                        <img src="/images/craft.svg" alt="Science Fair Winners">
                        <div class="news-date">
                            <span class="day">28</span>
                            <span class="month">Apr</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="news-content">
                        <h3>Science Fair Winners</h3>
                        <p>Congratulations to our brilliant students who won top prizes at the Regional Science Fair!</p>
                        <a href="#" class="read-more">Read More <i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i></a>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="news-item">
                    <div class="news-image">
                        <img src="/images/pta.svg" alt="Parent-Teacher Conference">
                        <div class="news-date">
                            <span class="day">05</span>
                            <span class="month">Jun</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="news-content">
                        <h3>Parent-Teacher Conference</h3>
                        <p>Our next Parent-Teacher Conference is scheduled for June 5th. Don't miss this opportunity to discuss your child's progress.</p>
                        <a href="#" class="read-more">Read More <i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i></a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="view-more-container">
                <a href="/Parent_resources/School_circular/school-circular.html" class="view-more-button">View More</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="testimonial-section">
        <div class="container">
            <h2>What Our Community Says</h2>
            <div class="testimonial-slider">
                <div class="testimonial-track">
                    <div class="testimonial-item">
                        <div class="testimonial-content">
                            <p>"Pearlworth Foundation School has been a blessing for our family. The teachers are dedicated, and the curriculum is challenging yet engaging."</p>
                            <div class="testimonial-author">
                                <img src="/images/Sarah.svg" alt="Sarah Johnson">
                                <span>Sarah Nakato, Parent</span>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="testimonial-item">
                        <div class="testimonial-content">
                            <p>"As a former student, I can confidently say that Pearlworth laid the foundation for my success. The values and skills I learned here have been invaluable."</p>
                            <div class="testimonial-author">
                                <img src="/images/Timothy.svg" alt="Michael Chen">
                                <span>Timothy Mugumya, Parent</span>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="testimonial-item">
                        <div class="testimonial-content">
                            <p>"The supportive community at Pearlworth is unparalleled. From the administration to the teachers and fellow parents, everyone is committed to the students' success."</p>
                            <div class="testimonial-author">
                                <img src="/images/Grace.svg" alt="Emily Rodriguez">
                                <span>Grace Praise, Parent</span>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="testimonial-nav">
                <button class="prev-testimonial">&lt;</button>
                <button class="next-testimonial">&gt;</button>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <%- include('partials/footer') %>


    <script src="/js/home.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
